    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Prayer Necessary to Right Decision</strong>&mdash;If men and women are in the habit of praying twice a day before they contemplate marriage, they should pray four times a day when such a step is anticipated. Marriage is something that will influence and affect your life, both in this world and in the world to come....",
