    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Confide in Godly Parents</strong>&mdash;If you are blessed with God-fearing parents, seek counsel of them. Open to them your hopes and plans; learn the lessons which their life experiences have taught.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 359.1\" data-link=\"135.1808\">The Ministry of Healing, 359</span>.</span></a></sup>",
